  <title>electron affinity</title>
  <termversion>2.3.3</termversion>
  <lastupdated>2014-02-24</lastupdated>
  <definitions>
    <item>
      <id>1</id>
      <text>Energy required to detach an electron from the singly charged negative ion (energy for the process [image: Not defined]). The equivalent more common definition is the energy released (E initial- E final) when an additional electron is attached to a neutral atom or molecule.</text>
      <chemicals>
        <item>
          <type>chemimage</type>
          <title>Not defined</title>
